---
import ToolsGrid from '../react/ToolsGrid';
---

<section class="py-16 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-brand-border/80 transition-colors">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-12">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="tools_title">彻底解耦的内置工具矩阵</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2" data-i18n="tools_subtitle">智能体在每一步 ReAct 循环中，将根据您的系统权限约束，挑选最合理的工具集进行组装。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0 flex gap-2 font-mono text-xs" aria-label="工具安全等级图例">
      <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-950/40 text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-900/50 rounded inline-flex items-center gap-1">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span data-i18n="tools_danger_label">危险工具 (危险指令弹框)</span>
      </span>
      <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-950/40 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-900/50 rounded inline-flex items-center gap-1">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span data-i18n="tools_safe_label">安全工具 (静默秒级返回)</span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ToolsGrid client:visible />
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">以上完整 22 个底层工具均提供严格的 TypeScript 类型声明与 IPC 安全策略映射。</span>
  </div>
</section>
